{
  "stem": "14060.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And each time, after a period of time when they became more well-to-do, they suddenly decided to chase them out from there and, therefore, confiscate their assets.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this went on in various periods.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in the Hungarian history, it is a black date in the Hungarian historical calendar of 1526, when the Turks beat the Hungarians in Mohacs, which is in southern Hungary and consequently occupied the country for 150 years.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The Turks, as you know, went up, right up to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But in the Jewish records of history, it is known to be the only golden period the Jews ever experienced in the country of Hungary.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you see, you must put things in the proper context of the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I grew up in what was generally a a sort of antisemitic but, nevertheless, in a indirect manner.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That means that people were allowed to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People were allowed to trade.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were not restricted as such in their activities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm talking, I presume, up to the mid '30s, and not later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "However, if I go back just 10 years before I was born, as you know, after the First World War Hungary had one of the first communist governments.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that happened to have been led by a Jew by the name of Bela Kun.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in 1920, Horthy, who was the head of state from that time right up till 1944, '45, was a-- what they called the White Terror.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were terrible atrocities against Jews committed in the name of the Hungarian people, simply by blaming the Jews for the short period of communism, which was quite like the Bolshevik Revolution.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Nevertheless, eventually that settled down and calmed down.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
